metadata.name: Genesis Shadow #001
metadata.description:
The light of the soul casts a shadow and dark beings are born out of it.

This Shadow was born out of heartache and loss, the first of its kind.

The Shadows can be paired with a Seeker to create a custom made Fallen being. The Shadows only have enough darkness to mentor one soul. 

To learn more about the project go to: https://www.jeyram.xyz/
